1. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper deals with a distributed model of communication for disseminating information in a network, which falls under the scope of distributed computing. 
2. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper discusses the spreading of rumors in a network, which is a topic of interest in social and information networks. 
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the dissemination of information in a network, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses a protocol for information dissemination in a network, which can be seen as a control problem in systems and control. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper presents technical results on the efficiency of the restricted pull protocol, which involves algorithmic analysis and can be seen as a topic of interest in data structures and algorithms.
